{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/108769", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/108769/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/108769/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/108769/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/108769", "id": 1610154695, "node_id": "I_kwDOAAsO6M5f-QLH", "number": 108769, "title": "`atan(tan(pi/2))` = `-pi/2` using `f32`", "user": {"login": "CanadaHonk", "id": 19228318, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE5MjI4MzE4", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/19228318?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/CanadaHonk", "html_url": "https://github.com/CanadaHonk", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/CanadaHonk/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/CanadaHonk/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/CanadaHonk/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/CanadaHonk/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/CanadaHonk/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/CanadaHonk/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/CanadaHonk/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/CanadaHonk/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/CanadaHonk/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 2139259423, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwyMTM5MjU5NDIz", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/A-floating-point", "name": "A-floating-point", "color": "f7e101", "default": false, "description": "Area: Floating point numbers and arithmetic"}], "state": "open", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 15, "created_at": "2023-03-05T11:04:26Z", "updated_at": "2023-04-19T03:37:59Z", "closed_at": null, "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "Doing the math expression `atan(tan(pi/2))` using `f32` gives `-pi/2` instead of `pi/2`.\r\n\r\nI tried this code:\r\n\r\n```rust\r\nfn main() {\r\n    println!(\"f32: {}\", (std::f32::consts::PI / 2.0).tan().atan());\r\n    println!(\"f64: {}\", (std::f64::consts::PI / 2.0f64).tan().atan());\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nI expected to see this happen:\r\n```\r\nf32: 1.5707963\r\nf64: 1.5707963267948966\r\n```\r\n\r\nInstead, this happened:\r\n```\r\nf32: -1.5707963\r\nf64: 1.5707963267948966\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Meta\r\nPlayground link: https://play.rust-lang.org/?version=stable&mode=debug&edition=2021&gist=7472c517d73a8e6ab0702feb2f8149d9\r\n", "closed_by": null, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/108769/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/108769/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null}